
The Net::FTP::Simple module provides a simplified interface for common
FTP tasks.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Makefile.PL
    make
    make test
    make install


DEPENDENCIES

    Net::FTP

For testing:
    Test::More
    Test::MockObject
    Test::Perl::Critic
    Test::Pod::Coverage
    Test::Pod

